{"tid":1572802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"戰！戰！戰！岳義士唔撚係想你地喊到成隻豬咁！而係報仇！","createTime":"2019-09-15T18:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T02:35:31.000Z","uid":4396,"like":127,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b617b6f6241f1f468a90185a83d1ba80113028a1","tid":1572802,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:42:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌你老母！岳義士捨生取義為既係咩？係對香港的愛呀！你地仲on99咁點對得住佢！全部人同我轉動你的腦！我地要港共政府、警犬、黑社會死！咪撚過第二日就忘記所有人的犧牲！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">全香港人</span>：見警犬、黑社會班畜生即刻還手！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">勇武</span>：快閃火魔法ok?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>：掩護勇武、做好文宣！咪撚做左膠！咪撚輸俾藍絲呀！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣</span>：集中宣傳警黑合作、929全球反共大遊行、10月1幫中共賀死忌！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">鍵盤戰士</span>：舉報藍絲fb page，入藍絲群做臥底！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">真。軍師（非冷氣）</span>：幫手檢討行動不足，如何佈局、如何撤退、如何升級裝備！<br />\n<br />\n依場係一場革命，唔係煮飯仔！會死人的！全部人一定要盡力做先可以贏！<br />\n<br />\n為香港，鞠躬盡瘁死而後已！<br />\n<br />\nHK forever!<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span>"},{"pid":"22c5432cddd133ec362a44f7ed7bec519d8bb40a","tid":1572802,"uid":147888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:43:42.000Z","msg":"tui<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60036e11cfdb6e4b8c5679250fbce9c5bd4dff4c","tid":1572802,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:45:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d0ce220519ad2b9c26c280b5bb70eef84f5c02","tid":1572802,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:53:23.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"f2e20d